2.20	Bharathi_Vishnuvardhan	Bharathi Vishnuvardhan	Bharathi Vishnuvardhan (Kannada: ಭಾರತಿ ವಿಷ್ಣುವರ್ಧನ್; born 15 January 1951) is an Indian actress who has performed in Kannada, Malayalam, Tamil and Telugu language films. She was most popular as an actress in the Kannada film industry during the late 1960s to 1980s.	
